# Security Configuration Example
# ==============================

# Google reCAPTCHA Configuration
# -----------------------------
# 1. Go to: https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin/
# 2. Click "+" to create a new site
# 3. Choose reCAPTCHA v2 > "I'm not a robot" Checkbox
# 4. Add domains:
#    - localhost (for development)
#    - kamotech.net (for production)
#    - www.kamotech.net
# 5. Copy the Site Key and Secret Key

RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your-recaptcha-site-key
RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=your-recaptcha-secret-key

# Brevo (Sendinblue) Email Configuration
# -------------------------------------
# 1. Sign up at: https://app.brevo.com/
# 2. Go to: https://app.brevo.com/settings/keys/smtp
# 3. Generate SMTP credentials
# 4. Copy the SMTP login (email) and password

MAIL_MAILER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=smtp-relay.brevo.com
MAIL_PORT=587
MAIL_USERNAME=your-brevo-smtp-email@example.com
MAIL_PASSWORD=your-brevo-smtp-password
MAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=noreply@kamotech.net
MAIL_FROM_NAME="${APP_NAME}"

# Important Notes:
# ---------------
# - reCAPTCHA is only shown for non-Google OAuth logins
# - OTP emails are sent via Brevo for email verification
# - OTP codes expire after 10 minutes
# - Users can resend OTP after 2 minutes
# - Maximum 5 OTP attempts per email